description.raw:
`FuelClient.Models` is failing on OSX and Windows. It was also failing for me locally, because I had files on the cache. So I changed the test to use a test cache instead of the default one, let's see if that helps.

Other changes:

* updated the `Models` and `Worlds` functions so that they don't make REST requests with URLs missing an owner.
* Added more world tests
* Made all `FuelClient` tests verbose
